  </section>

  <!-- Projects Section -->
  <section id="projects">
    <h2>Projects</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong><a href="https://aviasales.ru" target="_blank">Aviasales</a></strong> – developed the first versions of content and search engines. Played one of the key roles in the early stage of the company's development.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong><a href="https://travelpayouts.com" target="_blank">Travelpayouts</a></strong> – from the formation of the direction, first informally and then formally, was responsible for technology and the delivery process of the unit.
      </li>
